@{fg highlight}@{b}@{i}  Guide created with the Explorer 4.5 - AmigaGuide® CD Creator ! 
            © 1998 by Jochen Grus & Martin Gentile@{fg text}@{ub}@{ui}
-------------------------------------------------------------------

                   @{" Filelist of: WorkBench:22/444/55/ " }

@{b}If you don`t want to unpack DMS files to DF0: you must mount an
alternative device like RAD. @{ub}

-------------------------------------------------------------------
@{" Mount RAD " system " C:Mount rad: from WorkBench:Mountlist
 "}  @{" Mount FF0 " system "  C:Mount ff0: from WorkBench:Mountlist
 "}  @{" Mount FF1 " system "  C:Mount ff1: from WorkBench:Mountlist
 "}  @{" Mount FF2 " system "  C:Mount ff2: from WorkBench:Mountlist
 "}  @{" Mount FF3 " system "  C:Mount ff3: from WorkBench:Mountlist
 "}
-------------------------------------------------------------------

@{b}              Now you must assign the selected Device@{ub}

@{" Assign RAD " system " C:assign dmsdev: rad: 
 "} @{" Assign FF0 " system "  c:assign dmsdev: ff0: 
 "} @{" Assign FF1 " system "  C:assign dmsdev: ff1: 
 "} @{" Assign FF2 " system "  C:assign dmsdev: ff2: 
 "} @{" Assign FF3 " system "  C:assign dmsdev: ff3: 
 "}

-------------------------------------------------------------------
